WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.766
What are you doing?

2
00:00:03.366 --> 00:00:05.666
Miss you, don't get me wrong

3
00:00:05.766 --> 00:00:07.766
I have nothing to do with Yue Shen

4
00:00:07.766 --> 00:00:09.366
You have to believe me.

5
00:00:09.466 --> 00:00:11.900
I believe but I don't believe in you

6
00:00:11.900 --> 00:00:13.000
It's my husband

7
00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:14.966
Husband, are you done?

8
00:00:14.966 --> 00:00:16.366
Let's go eat.

9
00:00:16.366 --> 00:00:17.500
It's done.

10
00:00:17.666 --> 00:00:20.366
Yue Shen, won't you send me back?

11
00:00:20.366 --> 00:00:22.733
It's a long way to the pig farm

12
00:00:22.733 --> 00:00:24.433
My feet hurt when I walk

13
00:00:25.300 --> 00:00:26.066
Yue Shen

14
00:00:26.066 --> 00:00:29.166
I remember you mentioned that you were teammates with Comrade Yang

15
00:00:29.166 --> 00:00:30.466
Formerly in an army

16
00:00:30.766 --> 00:00:33.166
I was also fortunate to have been a soldier with Ye Shen

17
00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:34.600
Comrade Yang is right

18
00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:37.066
You do have a last name.

19
00:00:38.866 --> 00:00:41.166
Moon God, do you want to send me?

20
00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:44.400
You promised my brother to take good care of me

21
00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:47.266
I have arranged for Yu Dong to send you off, you go find him

22
00:00:47.333 --> 00:00:49.566
Why did you arrange me for someone else?

23
00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:52.500
I don't miss you, you're already an adult.

24
00:00:52.500 --> 00:00:54.700
Could you please stop being so petty?

25
00:00:55.700 --> 00:00:56.600
Why don't you send it?

26
00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:57.966
People in the province say I'm petty

27
00:00:57.966 --> 00:01:00.633
Since Comrade Yang is not satisfied with my arrangement

28
00:01:00.966 --> 00:01:02.166
Then do it yourself

29
00:01:02.200 --> 00:01:04.166
Hey, what did you give today?

30
00:01:04.166 --> 00:01:05.166
It smells so good.

31
00:01:05.866 --> 00:01:06.666
Shuyue ginseng

32
00:01:07.366 --> 00:01:09.266
Are you really ignoring me?

33
00:01:09.266 --> 00:01:12.066
Comrade Yang, you are already an adult

34
00:01:12.066 --> 00:01:13.900
Yue Shen just doesn't have time to send it to you.

35
00:01:13.900 --> 00:01:15.633
Why are you crying?

36
00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:17.233
About me and Yueshin

37
00:01:17.666 --> 00:01:18.966
What does it have to do with you?

38
00:01:20.266 --> 00:01:22.200
Nian Nian is my wife

39
00:01:27.933 --> 00:01:29.866
Don't talk to me if you're angry

